values:
This LiveJournal is for my friends.

Not Ex-wives ( THIS MEANS YOU JESSICA )

Not for Legal Counsel

Not for 11706 ( THIS MEANS YOU DR. ZIEMAN )

** This journal is the private thoughts and messages meant only for specific individuals who have been given access. The infinite thought process stuff I deal with on a daily basis is for humor, my peace of mind, my enjoyment.
Want to be my friend and read the crazy thoughts, you MUST ask.
You must not be a health care professional trying to use this blog to evaluate me.
You must not be an ex wife, or member of her family.
You must not be a member of the law enforcement community.
